<h2>Chapter 5: Sentiment and On-Page SEO &#123;#ch5&#125;</h2>
<p>Sentiment analysis does not just monitor what others say. It improves the content you create.</p>
<h3>Matching Content Tone to Search Intent</h3>
<p>Different queries expect different emotional tones. Sentiment analysis helps you match that expectation.</p>
